<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Death Ponee</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Boogaloo&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0a0a0a, #1a1a1a);
        color: #ffcf00;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem 1rem;
      }

      section {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
      }

      #home {
        padding-bottom: 6rem;
      }
      #home h2 {
        color: #cccccc;
        white-space: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
      }

      #about {
        padding-top: 5rem;
      }

      #about p {
        color: #e0e0d8; /* or try #f0eade */
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 1rem auto;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: justify;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }

      #about h2 {
        color: #ffcf00;
      }

      #who {
        padding-top: 5rem;
      }

      .band-members {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 1rem auto;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: justify;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }

      .band-members .member {
        max-width: 600px; /* Match .bio-text width exactly */
        margin: 1rem auto;
        color: #f0eade;
        text-align: justify;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }

      .name {
        color: #ffcf00;
        font-weight: bold;
      }


      h1 {
        font-family: 'Boogaloo', sans-serif;
        font-size: 6rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #ffcf00;
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: 'Boogaloo', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #ffcf00;
      }
      .subheading {
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #f0eade;
        font-weight: bold; 
        white-space: nowrap;       /* Prevents line breaks */
        overflow: hidden;          /* Hides overflow */
        text-overflow: ellipsis;   /* Adds "…" if text is too long */
      }

      .album-covers {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      .album-covers img {
        max-width: 300px;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #000;
      }

      @keyframes glitch {
        0% { filter: contrast(1) brightness(1); }
        20% { filter: contrast(1.1) brightness(1.1); }
        40% { filter: contrast(1.2) brightness(0.9); }
        60% { filter: contrast(1.1) brightness(1); }
        80% { filter: contrast(1) brightness(1.2); }
        100% { filter: contrast(1) brightness(1); }
      }

      .album-covers img {
        animation: glitch 1.4s infinite;
        image-rendering: pixelated;
        transition: filter 0.2s;
      }

      .links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .links a {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #252525;
        color: #ffcf00;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid #ffcf00;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .links a:hover {
        background-color: #ffcf00;
        color: #000;
      }

      .band-photo {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .band-photo img {
        width: 600px;
        max-width: 90%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 207, 0, 0.15);
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease forwards;
      }
      .bio-text {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: justify;
        color: #f0eade;
     }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        to { opacity: 1; }
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 3rem;
          letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        h2 {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .album-covers img {
          max-width: 45%;
        }

        .links {
          flex-wrap: nowrap;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .links a {
          font-size: 0.8rem;
          padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
          white-space: nowrap;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="home">
      <h1>Death Ponee</h1>
      <div class="subheading">New album: <em>Waiting for Rover</em> – out now!</div>

      <div class="album-covers">
        <img src="/Final Front copy_for Digital (2).jpg" alt="Album cover front" />
        <img src="/Final Back copy_for Digital.jpg" alt="Album cover back" />
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/7DLH0CwDNEX6SX8OLLb3H5" target="_blank">Spotify</a>
        <a href="https://music.apple.com/us/album/waiting-for-rover-ep/1822589894" target="_blank">Apple Music</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_lqEcVBijeakOThABs2QHeLU7wPVUiZ3EU" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
        <a href="https://music.amazon.com/albums/B0FF6TZ33Q" target="_blank">Amazon</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BIO SECTION -->
    <section id="about">
  <h2>What are we?</h2>

  <div class="band-photo">
    <img src="/Band photo2.png" alt="Death Ponee band photo" />
  </div>

  <div class="bio-text">
    <p><strong class="name">Death Ponee is an electronic post-punk band from Prague, built on live synths, searing guitars, and uptempo drums.</strong></p>

    <p>It started with me — a cellist-turned-synth player — writing moody tracks on a digital piano and wanting to build something raw and live. I called up people I’d played with before, picked up a synth, and we got to work.</p>

    <p>Our first album, <em>Life’s Great Uniform</em>, was instrumental. On <em>Waiting for Rover</em>, I step up to the mic for the first time. We’re now a four-piece: two synths, guitar, drums, and a tiny 8-bit sampler called the MicroGranny making weird noises at the edge of everything.</p>
  </div>
</section> 
<section id="who">
  <h2>Who are we?</h2>
  <div class="band-members">
    <div class="member">
      <span class="name">Matt Ford</span> – Synths, vocals, and occasional existential dread. Former cellist, now armed with circuits and sarcasm. British, but slowly assimilating.
    </div>
    <div class="member">
      <span class="name">Mark Tierney</span> – Guitarist. Never seems to age — possibly immortal. Thinks fuzz pedals are a food group.
    </div>
    <div class="member">
      <span class="name">George Allen</span> – Synths and vocals. Meticulous, melodic, and almost certainly has a colour-coded band spreadsheet.
    </div>
    <div class="member">
      <span class="name">Nick Jennings</span> – Drums. Solid as a rock. Possibly the banjo king of Prague — but we try not to encourage him.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  </body>
</html>
